    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cfd-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to level 1 per MRL 2 guidance. RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied at all five operating points (RH range 0.71–0.94). Discretization error (GCI < 5%) and pressure-rise validation (error < 8%) provide sufficient confidence in model fidelity for the COU. The qualitative treatment of inter-donor biological variability in the hemolysis validation is noted as a limitation of the current evidence package but does not preclude acceptance at MRL 2 given the conservative RH margin observed.",
